/*> c.DOSnaming <*/
/*---------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
/* MSDOS to RISCOS name conversion                Copyright (c) 1989 JGSmith */
/*---------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
/* RISC OS name:
 *      [$.]<path>
 * RISC OS path:
 *      <filename (max. 10 chars)>[.<path element>]
 *
 * DOS name:
 *      [\]<path>
 * DOS path:
 *      <filename (max. 8 chars)>[.<extension (max. 3 chars)>[\<path element>]
 */
/*---------------------------------------------------------------------------*/

